OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has been told he
OL,7,Fmust scrap plans to "hammer" families
OL,8,Fby raising the price for passports to
OL,9,Fmore than #100.
OL,11,FThe SNP said Sir Keir Starmer must not
OL,12,Fallow inflation-busting price rises to
OL,13,Fgo ahead at a time when the cost of
OL,14,Fliving is already growing.
OL,16,FUnder the proposals, the application
OL,17,Ffee for an online passport would rise
OL,18,Ffrom #94.50 to #102 for an adult and
OL,19,F#61.50 to #66.50 for a child ` an
OL,20,Fincrease of 8%.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@\O]
