OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,FAdults applying by post would see
OL,7,Ftheir fees rise from #107 to #115.50
OL,8,Fwhile the cost for a child would
OL,9,Fincrease from #74 to #80.
OL,11,FThe plans will go ahead on April 8 if
OL,12,Fapproved by Parliament and the SNP
OL,13,Fsaid it would vote against the
OL,14,Fproposals.
OL,16,FThe Home Office has said the plans
OL,17,Fwould ensure the costs of the system
OL,18,Frely less on taxpayers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
