OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,FAnalysis by the House of Commons
OL,7,FLibrary, commissioned by the SNP,
OL,8,Fshows the cost of a standard UK adult
OL,9,Fpassport by post will have increased
OL,10,Fby 542% since 1997, from #18 to
OL,11,F#115.50.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the cost of a child's
OL,14,Fpassport by post will have increased
OL,15,Fby 627% since 1999 ` up from #11 to
OL,16,F#80.
OL,18,FIn the same period, the analysis shows
OL,19,Fwages have only increased by 144%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
