OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774235555
OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,FIf prices had instead increased in
OL,7,Fline with inflation, an adult passport
OL,8,Fwould only cost #33.36 from April and
OL,9,Fa children's passport would cost
OL,10,F#21.60, according to the analysis.
OL,12,FThe SNP said Labour's price hike would
OL,13,Fsee a family of four charged up to
OL,14,F#391 to purchase two adult and two
OL,15,Fchildren's passports ` the equivalent
OL,16,Fof around a whole week's wages for
OL,17,Fsomeone on the minimum wage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
