OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,FMr Wishart, the party's MP for Perth
OL,7,Fand Kinross-shire, said: "The Labour
OL,8,FParty must not hammer families with
OL,9,Fanother massive, inflation-busting
OL,10,Fhike in passport fees when the cost of
OL,11,Fliving is already soaring on Keir
OL,12,FStarmer's watch.
OL,14,F"Under the Labour Government, energy
OL,15,Fbills are #500 higher than promised,
OL,16,Ffood and fuel prices have gone through
OL,17,Fthe roof, mortgage rates are rising
OL,18,Fagain, UK unemployment is at a five-
OL,19,Fyear high and hard-pressed families
OL,20,Fare already struggling to get by.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOU
