OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer is completely out of
OL,7,Ftouch if he thinks households want him
OL,8,Fto press ahead with more tone-deaf
OL,9,FLabour Party price hikes, which will
OL,10,Fincrease the cost of a family holiday
OL,11,Fand make it more expensive for
OL,12,FScotland fans to travel to the World
OL,13,FCup this summer.
OL,15,F"The SNP will vote against this
OL,16,Funacceptable price hike.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
