OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,F"While the Labour Party is making life
OL,7,Feven harder for families, the SNP is
OL,8,Fdetermined to do everything we can to
OL,9,Fhelp, which is why we've delivered the
OL,10,Fstrongest cost-of-living support
OL,11,Fpackage for households in the UK and
OL,12,Fwill continue to put money back into
OL,13,Fpeople's pockets under John Swinney's
OL,14,Fleadership."
OL,16,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,17,FGovernment does not make any profit
OL,18,Ffrom the cost of passport applications.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]xD@bOU
