OL,3,CDo not hammer families with massive
OL,4,Cpassport price hike, SNP tells Starmer
OL,6,F"The fee for a standard online
OL,7,Fapplication made within the UK will
OL,8,Frise to #102, while the fee for postal
OL,9,Fapplications will rise by the same
OL,10,Fincrease, which remains around 8%.
OL,12,F"The new fees will help the Home
OL,13,FOffice to continue to move towards a
OL,14,Fsystem that meets its costs through
OL,15,Fthose who use it, reducing reliance on
OL,16,Ffunding from general taxation."
